# NXtutors WhatsApp Onboarding Agent - GitHub Setup Status

## Add Environment Secrets Manually

GitHub path:

```text
Repository -> Settings -> Environments -> dev/staging/prod -> Environment secrets
```

GitHub secrets cannot be blank in the UI. Use this as a checklist and paste the real value for each key.

### dev Environment secrets

```env
APP_KEY=
DB_HOST=
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=
DB_USERNAME=
DB_PASSWORD=

META_WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=
META_WHATSAPP_APP_SECRET=
META_WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN=
META_WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID=
```

### staging Environment secrets

```env
APP_KEY=
DB_HOST=
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=
DB_USERNAME=
DB_PASSWORD=

META_WHATSAPP_VERIFY_TOKEN=
META_WHATSAPP_APP_SECRET=
META_WHATSAPP_ACCESS_TOKEN=
